track_notes: By this time of the year you can park at the Madone de Fenestre, many room on summit for antenna. The walk is not difficult, good shoes needed.
Must check that path is still good, since Alex storm, it may be dangerous to walk some places
This is a nice summit, snowshoes in winter and plenty water in summer. since the alex storm, the path may be affected!
Done in summer, 2 hours up, 1 hour and 15mn to go down.
